3. Rehydrate sample(s) in phosphate-buffered saline (PBS) for 5 min at room temperature.
4. Apply secondary fixative, Bouin’s solution, for 1 h at 56°C. PrewarmBouin’s solutionto60°C.Thisstepmayalsobeperformedatroomtemperature overnight.NotethatBouin’ssolutionisveryhazardousandmustbeusedin chemicalhood.ConsultMSDSpriortouse.
