FIG. 2.
Scanning electron micrographs of murine peritoneal collagen. C57B1/6 murine peritoneal tissue explants were dissected with collagen layer exposed, subjected to SEM processing as described in the text, and imaged with FEI-Magellan 400 field emission microscope. Scale bars are equal to 50, 10, and 2 μm for A, B, and C, respectively.
