Trichrome staining of oral gingiva of rabbits. Rabbits’ gingival tissues were extracted and processed using Masson’s Trichrome. Collagen stains blueand the nuclei are stained dark brown.The muscle tissue is stained redand cytoplasm is stainedpink.This example was prepared as detailed in the text. Scale bar is 600μm.
