OVCAR5 and OVCAR8 ovarian cancer cell invasion of three-dimensional Matrigel© and collagen gels. Samples were prepared as detailed in the respective invasion assay section in the text and allowed to incubate for 24 h, after which they were imaged at 10 × magnification. Scale bars are equal to 200μm.
